{"ID":"20260305082130-gf29u2c","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gf29u2c","tags":"课程/CPP程序设计","title":"虚函数","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-ctf9qol","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-ctf9qol"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntags:\n  - 课程/CPP程序设计\ntitle: 虚函数\ndate created: 星期六, 十月 18日 2025, 4:55:45 下午\ndate modified: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 11:48:21 晚上\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zequ7y8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zequ7y8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚函数是 C++ 实现"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运行时多态"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的核心机制。它是连接继承和多态的桥梁。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-eoq5tco","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-eoq5tco","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 虚函数的定义"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-t71nder","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-t71nder","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚函数是在 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082131-2dyp7kf","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"基类"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中声明的，用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠virtual"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 关键字修饰的成员函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-nsmli5x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-nsmli5x","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"定义方式："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（在体外实现时，不需要加 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"virtual"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-lxvx7a3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-lxvx7a3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"class Base {\npublic: // 声明为 public 或 protedted 都可以\n    virtual ReturnType functionName(Parameters); // 声明为虚函数\n    // ...\n};\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-k0i23cm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-k0i23cm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"接下来，在派生类中定义同名函数即可，添加 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"virtual"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 与否都是虚函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-df5qiza","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-df5qiza","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以在末尾加上关键字 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"override"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-6rv3rpf","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6rv3rpf","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ty5uge6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ty5uge6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-avw0l27","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-avw0l27","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"目的："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 明确告知编译器，派生类中的这个函数是旨在重写基类中的虚函数；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ix5szk7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ix5szk7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-3le0wpw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3le0wpw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"好处："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 编译器会检查基类中是否存在一个同名、同参数列表、同 ⁠const 属性的虚函数。如果不存在，编译器会报错，从而避免了因拼写错误、参数不匹配等原因导致的意外函数隐藏（而不是重写）问题。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zj5ive5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zj5ive5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 虚函数的作用"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-avhaap7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-avhaap7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e基类指针\u003c/font\u003e指向派生类成员并调用虚函数时，会根据成员的类型，动态的调用派生类中定义的函数。如果未定义 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"virtual"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，则始终调用基类函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-y2ddt73","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-y2ddt73","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注意，不是使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"public"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 派生控制时，即非 [[父类和子类]] 关系时，需要使用强制类型转换使用基类指针指向派生类："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"base *ptr_base = (base *) \u0026amp;obj_derived;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。建议使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"public"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 派生控制。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ik4hn2d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ik4hn2d","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e父类指针指向子类对象时，虚函数的功效才显现出来。\u003c/font\u003e"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-bvhe264","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-bvhe264","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-uzb8b8y","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-uzb8b8y","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-czzeplr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-czzeplr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译按定义的类型（表象）来执行检查；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-i8wg3as","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-i8wg3as","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-gp6b8xr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gp6b8xr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数调用是根据\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e虚函数表\u003c/font\u003e找入口地址，找到的是实际指向对象的函数地址（本质）。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-pyyrdd5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-pyyrdd5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以通过作用域限定符 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"::"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 来访问虚函数，绕过运行时多态。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-l6h7blg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l6h7blg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚函数 vs 函数重载："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-8t1l6di","Type":"NodeTable","Data":"| 虚函数          | 函数重载          |\n| ------------ | ------------- |\n| 函数名、参数、返回值相同 | 函数名相同，参数不同    |\n| 只能是成员函数      | 可以是成员函数和非成员函数 |\n| 根据对象调用不同的虚函数 | 根据参数调用不同的重载函数 |","TableAligns":[0,0],"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8t1l6di","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚函数"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数重载"}]}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数名、参数、返回值相同"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数名相同，参数不同"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只能是成员函数"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以是成员函数和非成员函数"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","TableAligns":[0,0],"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据对象调用不同的虚函数"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据参数调用不同的重载函数"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-xop13fz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xop13fz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 虚函数的工作原理"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-qpr7r2w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qpr7r2w","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C++ 标准没有强制规定虚函数的具体实现机制，但主流编译器都采用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚函数表 (Virtual Table, vtable)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚指针 (Virtual Pointer, vptr)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的机制来实现运行时多态。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-4h0foem","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-4h0foem","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.1 虚函数表 vtable"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-u35cpq0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u35cpq0","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每个含有虚函数的类（或其派生类）都会在编译时生成一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚函数表"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。vtable 是一个函数指针数组，其中存储了该类所有虚函数的地址。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果派生类重写了某个虚函数，vtable 中对应的条目就会指向派生类中的实现；否则，它会指向基类中的实现。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1obpf6f","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1obpf6f","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.2 虚指针 vptr"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-idt8e5k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-idt8e5k","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每个含有虚函数的类的对象，都会在其实例中包含一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"虚指针"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这个 vptr 是对象的一部分，它指向该对象所属类的 vtable。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-23pqeqj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-23pqeqj","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运行时查找过程："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 当通过基类指针调用虚函数时，程序会"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-6su3iie","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6su3iie","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-aaa1a96","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-aaa1a96","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-fsjecez","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fsjecez","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通过基类指针找到对象的 vptr。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-mi6by4d","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mi6by4d","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-9uuzbmo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9uuzbmo","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通过 vptr 找到对象的 vtable 。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-xm2si2d","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xm2si2d","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-zy5y1q3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zy5y1q3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在 vtable 中查找对应虚函数的地址。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dnddyrv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dnddyrv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-kucljpy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-kucljpy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"调用该地址处 vptr 的函数。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个查找过程发生在运行时，因此实现了动态绑定。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-xshza7e","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xshza7e","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4 虚析构函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-oaqeo8e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-oaqeo8e","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"构造函数不能定义为虚函数，而析构函数可以定义为虚函数：派生类的析构函数可通过父类指针、引用或 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"delete"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 调用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-l5qfykf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l5qfykf","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用虚析构函数的好处：在使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"delete"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 运算符删除一个对象时，保证执行的析构函数就是该对象自己的析构函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zus340m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zus340m","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"执行过程："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果将基类析构函数定义为虚函时，那么通过父类指针、引用析构时，首先调用派生类的析构函数，然后调用基类的析构函数，来确保所有内存空间均被释放。"}]}]}